u%C3%A2n/poem-gITTt81GU-HXgS7FHzqY6g">Tặng Uông Luân - 贈汪倫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Tr%C3%A0o-L%E1%BB%97-nho/poem-UttU-9GPupDa2QzBbXNxmg">Trào Lỗ nho - 嘲魯儒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Nguy%E1%BB%87t-Anh/T%E1%BB%B1-ho%C3%A0i/poem-0Dsu8m-n85dJPoSfWO_giw">Tự hoài - 敘懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Nguy%E1%BB%87t-Anh/author-Etl4IImmKFqErJL8B4U-xw">Từ Nguyệt Anh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/V%E1%BB%8Dng-Phu-th%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-6vjNh-xjrQmniMVaD32snA">Vọng Phu thạch - 望夫石</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br></div>	</div>
